ğŸ“˜ Usage Guidelines

Consistency: Always use the same phrasing for similar contexts.

Clarity: Avoid ambiguity; messages should be instantly understandable.

Tone: Professional, supportive, and developer-focused.

Placement: Tooltips on hover/tap, errors inline near fields, success confirmations as banners or toasts.

